column3: Primary ModelPrimary ModelThis is the primary model used by the agent. In some cases, an embedding model is used for RAG, or a secondary model like GPT-4o for image processing.Note:For non-OpenAI reasoning models, the reasoning token budget is set at 1,024 (low), 2,048 (medium), and 4,096 (high).
column4: VerifiedVerified ResultsResults have been reproduced by the HAL team
column5: AccuracyAccuracyConfidence intervals show the min-max values across runs for those agents where multiple runs are available
column6: Cost (USD)Total CostTotal API cost for running the agent on all tasks. Confidence intervals show the min-max values across runs for those agents where multiple runs are available
column7: RunsNumber of RunsThe number of runs for this agent submitted to the leaderboard. To submit multiple evaluations, rerun the same agent and set the same agent name
